            <div class="title">
                Hungary (Political Situation)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-06-12/debates/f126e18e-5184-4416-9669-3c4877dbdf35/BusinessOfTheHouse" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
