        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is the right hon. Gentleman aware that it was reported to me in Budapest in May, 1946, that these circumstances would arise on 1st May this year and that events have proved that my information was accurate on that occasion 12 months ago?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
